JWT Authentication config, setup
Add JWT vendor      -> composer require firebase/php-jwt
Add Authenticate    -> composer require cakephp/authentication

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Demo Cache:

{{host}}/api/v2/courses/get_all.json?language=zh_HK
-> get all will ADD to Cache (cake_course_getAll)

{{host}}/api/v1/courses/add_data.json
-> get add new data and DELETE store from Cache (cake_course_getAll)

